Posted By: Iggy
I have for sale a "100" card lot of T206 cards!  Mostly different but with a couple of dupes.

Price for the lot is $1400 which includes insured shipping.
NO Paypal, unless you want to cover the 3% fee ($40.90), checks or money orders are fine.

My email is: agonzdude@yahoo.com and for reference my ebay-id is iggy-man .

These are lower grade with "4" hall of famers and "1" beat-up A.O. Jordan southern leaguer.  The backs are all commons with three American Beauties and a few Polar Bear's.   Bid with confidence and good luck!

-Lovely Day...
